---
title: Smart Ground Pork Al Pastor-Inspired Salad with Chipotle Sauce and Crispy Shallots
description: In this taco-inspired salad, spiced pork and pineapple are tossed with dressed spinach but it's the topping that make this dish a true stand-out: feta, crispy shallots, guacamole and cilantro. Dress it however you like!
